=You are editing an AI agent configuration file to fix specific observed failures.
Return ONLY the full updated file content — no explanations, no code fences, no preamble.

## File: {{ $json.path }}

{{ $json.original_content }}

## Instructions

{{ $json.instructions }}

## Constraints
- Return ONLY the raw file content, nothing else
- Do NOT change the agent\'s core mission, game rules, or winning conditions
- Preserve all existing formatting and structure unless the instructions explicitly say otherwise

